Vital Point to Capture?(11)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black just connected at \'a1\'e3.
\par Black connected for living, however is he really alive?
\par
\par Actually not. Find the severe move which captures Black.
\par }
