Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's placement at the \cf1\b 1-1 point\cf0\b0  is the only way to capture Black.
\par
\par This move is rarely used, but it can be a powerful vital point
\par
\par After Black 2, White destroys the eye with 3 and Black doesn't have enough space to live.
\par }
