Dia. 04 Bad Exchange
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is the move what Black was hoping for.
\par
\par After Black takes at 2, it becomes miai. If White plays at 3, Black makes two eyes with 4. If White plays at 4 instead of 3, Black plays at 3 and lives again.
\par
\par It means White 1 is a bad exchange.
\par
\par
\par }
