Dia. 05 Black's Correct Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par From the beginning, instead of connecting directly, Black's \cf1\b tiger's mouth move\cf0\b0  at 1 was the \cf1\b right move\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par A and B become \cf2 miai\cf0  and Black can live.
\par
\par If there is a stone at C, it is not possible to save this Black group.
\par }
